metadata.name: Ascension
metadata.description:
Ascension, a journey to the stars  
Leaving behind our home and past  
We ascend to a new world  
Below fades away, a distant memory  
As we rise higher and higher, our spirits are free  
The air grows thin, the view expands  
We reach for the sky, our hearts full of hope  
We are weightless and free, unbound by gravity  
Our spirits soar, our stories untold  
We are reborn, in this moment of ascension  
We are more than just flesh and bone  
As we ascend, to a new beginning, to new heights, to new friends
